ackdrop_1800x700.png", "id": "521591527456037", "image_type": "APP_IMG_IMMERSIVE_LAYER_BACKDROP", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984458_521591530789370_8503274857588056658_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=C1arrgHvAdQQ7kNvgHyXUwX&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA29C0cy_jU6qstGy03EVxx-ayM-U9h9bboSsuwFVIMkw&oe=671B87AA"}]}, "id": "552272570543390", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "Screenshot_01.png", "id": "1464988294173192", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75303840_1464988297506525_8991340839166974651_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=o3hyckIhDmQQ7kNvgGd4WUW&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCBThHB2VTvPcwrvJwvDox9RTf7PUPbyAJc8u9rTOKmSQ&oe=671B9BC9"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot_02.png", "id": "998108822001177", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036669_998108825334510_8112152864798222185_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=KkZxTr7bLScQ7kNvgEc68Jz&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCyAQbygcPxrENCzs98H_VYhVA3H5OMbWENvwYV_cw-_g&oe=671B7A80"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot_03.png", "id": "1074895857368260", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/86610711_1074895860701593_7275850341165404444_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=3DArVWRCg1EQ7kNvgG79Iqn&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBH_8VLgw1UEA77MKDh0ATpyB8pKZfb8KMJcDtwOuvYow&oe=671B7517"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot_04.png", "id": "319481737914327", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75240109_319481741247660_2311776443441155712_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=mn0zLmiJd-MQ7kNvgGTX9z8&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAMK2ty5ooMbRq4K_3yM7X6gkWkmrHkLjlJhF5kHEmdJQ&oe=671B84FA"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot_05.png", "id": "1218222189322091", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974829_1218222192655424_6704110728869486582_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=aAq9UDyAMXoQ7kNvgHn_4CO&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAzHfaxax-zxIjuipa293YE35Xl_d_Qj_0O13Mg5YkhUw&oe=671B701C"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "JumpWorld_Cover_Landscape.png", "id": "1630745394490612", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75203626_1630745397823945_773068501026464412_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=JokWzxRihC0Q7kNvgGwdwMM&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDKaJJGWMLQFVpr38JqWA60qomZLaDFnZ9BSjGrjRZzfg&oe=671B82E2"}, "display_name": "Jump World", "keywords": ["Platformer", "racing", "fantasy", "obstacle", "course"], "long_description": "# The Obstacle Course Game You\u2019ve Been Waiting For!\n\n**RUN, JUMP, PUNCH & SMASH** your way through 40+ levels and dungeons in this retro-themed VR platformer & obstacle course game. Filled with tough challenges, inventive obstacles, treasures to collect and secrets to discover.\n\n{465167516542056}\n\n# 7 Worlds To Discover\n\n- Honeywood Hills\n- Cookie Crumble\n- Sky Brick Road\n- Jump N' Jammy\n- Arctic Freeze\n- Dark Citadel \n- Cybertron\n\n{519192847571723}\n\n# Easy To Pickup And Play\n\n- Play Seated or Standing.\n- Movement - Left & Right Thumbsticks.\n- Jump - A Button or Click Right Thumbstick.\n- Dash - Click Left Thumbstick.\n- Ground Smash - While in Air, Press Trigger.\n\n{467766532286204}\n# Face the final challenge. Enter each of the 7 Dungeons and see if you have what it takes to unlock the next world.\n- Untimed so you can progress at your own pace.\n- Reach the gates to unlock checkpoints.\n- Dungeons designed with platforming in mind.\n\n{543457814936511}\n# Race To The Finish Line!\n- Race against your own time.\n- Compete to achieve Bronze, Silver or Gold Trophies!\n- You aren't penalized for a lack of skill.\n- As long as you can complete each course, you can progress!\n- Keep practicing and you'll do GREAT!", "short_description": "RUN, JUMP, PUNCH & SMASH